description         Convert AsciiDoc documents to PDF using web technologies
long_description    ${name} is a PDF converter for AsciiDoc based on web \
                    technologies. It allows complex layouts to be defined with \
                    CSS and JavaScript, while writing the content in AsciiDoc. \
                    ${name} has support for LaTeX-style mathematical equations \
                    via MathJax, and syntax highlighting via highlight.js. \
                    Many more features can be added by importing an existing \
                    JavaScript or CSS framework.
